00:01:09,760 --> 00:01:12,130
MIGUEL: <i>Sometimes,
I think I'm cursed.</i>

4
00:01:12,130 --> 00:01:15,770
<i>Because of something that
happened before I was even born.</i>

5
00:01:15,770 --> 00:01:19,120
<i>See, a long time ago,
there was this family.</i>

6
00:01:20,270 --> 00:01:23,140
<i>The</i> papa, <i>he was a musician.</i>

7
00:01:23,140 --> 00:01:26,990
<i>He and his family would sing and
dance and count their blessings.</i>

8
00:01:28,150 --> 00:01:31,780
<i>But he also had a dream.
To play for the world.</i>

9
00:01:31,780 --> 00:01:33,630
