13
00:01:49,430 --> 00:01:51,170
<i>And the</i> mama...

14
00:01:51,170 --> 00:01:53,840
<i>She didn't have time to cry
over that walk-away musician.</i>

15
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:56,310
