39
00:03:12,820 --> 00:03:15,350
How are you, Julio?

40
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:17,520
<i>Actually, my name is Miguel.</i>

41
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:21,360
Mama <i>Coco has trouble
remembering things.</i>

42
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:23,390
<i>But it's good
to talk to her anyway.</i>

43
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:25,530
<i>So, I tell her
pretty much everything.</i>

44
