46
00:03:30,270 --> 00:03:34,440
And the winner
is <i>Luchadora</i> Coco!

47
00:03:34,440 --> 00:03:36,570
I have a dimple on this side,
but not on this side.

48
00:03:36,580 --> 00:03:38,540
Dimple, no dimple.
Dimple, no dimple.

49
00:03:38,540 --> 00:03:40,780
Miguel, eat your food.

50
00:03:40,780 --> 00:03:43,410
MIGUEL: <i>My</i> abuelita,
<i>she's</i> Mama <i>Coco's daughter.</i>

51
00:03:43,420 --> 00:03:46,550
Oh, you're a twig, <i>mijo.</i>
Have some more.

52
00:03:46,550 --> 00:03:47,680
No, <i>gracias.</i>

53
