63
00:04:06,710 --> 00:04:08,010
- No music!
- (MEN SCREAMING)

64
00:04:08,010 --> 00:04:10,440
MIGUEL: <i>I think we're
the only family in Mexico</i>

65
00:04:10,440 --> 00:04:12,410
<i>who hates music.</i>

66
00:04:12,410 --> 00:04:15,410
<i>And my family's fine
with that. But me...</i>

67
00:04:15,410 --> 00:04:17,760
- Be back by lunch, <i>mijo.</i>
- Love you, <i>Mama.</i>

68
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:21,330
<i>I am not like
the rest of my family!</i>

69
00:04:22,590 --> 00:04:23,990
- <i>Hola,</i> Miguel!
<i>- Hola!</i>

70
00:04:23,990 --> 00:04:26,910
(PLAYING MARIACHI MUSIC)

71
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:32,180
<i>- Muchas gracias.</i>
- <i>De nada,</i> Miguel.

72
00:04:36,100 --> 00:04:38,750
- (BARKS)
- Hey! Dante!

73
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:43,920
Sit. Down.
Roll over. Shake.

74
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:45,710
Fist bump!

75
00:04:45,710 --> 00:04:47,930
Good boy, Dante!

76
00:04:51,580 --> 00:04:54,120
<i>I know I'm not
supposed to love music.</i>

77
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:57,690
(CHUCKLES) <i>But it's not my fault!
It's his!</i>

78
00:04:57,690 --> 00:04:59,590
<i>Ernesto de la Cruz.</i>

79
00:04:59,590 --> 00:05:02,530
<i>The greatest musician
of all time.</i>

80
00:05:02,530 --> 00:05:04,460
TOUR GUIDE: Right here
in this very plaza,

81
00:05:04,460 --> 00:05:08,030
Ernesto de la Cruz
took his first steps...

82
00:05:08,030 --> 00:05:12,600
toward becoming the most beloved
singer in Mexican history.

83
00:05:12,610 --> 00:05:17,510
MIGUEL: <i>He started out a total
nobody from Santa Cecilia, like me.</i>

84
00:05:17,510 --> 00:05:21,550
<i>But when he played music, he made
people fall in love with him.</i>

85
00:05:21,550 --> 00:05:24,650
- (HORSE NEIGHING)
- <i>He starred in movies.</i>

86
00:05:24,650 --> 00:05:28,950
<i>He had the coolest guitar!
He could fly!</i>

87
00:05:28,950 --> 00:05:31,520
<i>And he wrote the best songs.</i>

88
00:05:31,520 --> 00:05:33,760
<i>But my all-time favorite,
it's...</i>

89
00:05:33,760 --> 00:05:35,790
<i>♪ Remember me</i>

90
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:37,060
<i>♪ Remember me</i>

91
00:05:37,060 --> 00:05:38,930
<i>♪ Though I have
