<i>- ♪ Remember me
- ♪ Remember me</i>

93
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:44,700
<i>♪ Don't let it make you cry
For even if I'm far away</i>

94
00:05:44,700 --> 00:05:48,410
<i>♪ I hold you in my heart
I sing a secret song to you</i>

95
00:05:48,410 --> 00:05:51,410
<i>♪ Each night we are apart
Remember me</i>

96
00:05:51,410 --> 00:05:53,410
<i>♪ Though I have
